function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	local tNearbySpawnLocs = Hydra.FindSpawnLocsNearPlayer(idActorDetector, "Dungeon_Monster", 0, 4, false, false)
	
	--Then 
	
	if tNearbySpawnLocs[1] ~= nil then
		--User function (Finds spawn locs near TRIGGER)
		UF_FindSpawnLocation(idSelf, tNearbySpawnLocs)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	local tNearbySpawnLocs = Hydra.FindSpawnLocsNearPlayer(idActorDetector, "Dungeon_Monster", 4, 8, false, false)
	
	
	
	--Then 
	
	if tNearbySpawnLocs[1] ~= nil then
		--User function (Finds spawn locs near SHRINE)
		UF_FindSpawnLocation(idSelf, tNearbySpawnLocs)
	else
		Hydra.EventSend("Defaced Shrine Spawn Failed", idSelf)
	end
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idShrine)
	
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idBrokenShrine)
	
	UF_CleanUp(idSelf)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorReceptacle)
	--Give the fx time to play
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idShrine)
	
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idBrokenShrine)

end

unk_c47e01a.value:
function UF_FindSpawnLocation(idSelf, tNearbySpawnLocs)
	local nRandLoc = Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, #tNearbySpawnLocs)
	
	local idMarkerLoc = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_MARKERLOCATION, tNearbySpawnLocs[nRandLoc])

	Hydra.ActorSpawnCarryable(S_CARRYABLE_DEFACED_SHRINE, idMarkerLoc)
	
	Hydra.EventSend("Defaced Shrine Spawn Successful", idSelf)
end

function UF_CleanUp(idSelf)
	tTriggers = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "SPAWN")
	
	for i, idTrigger in pairs(tTriggers) do
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idTrigger)
	end
end
